<p>I want to compare two matrices</p>  <pre><code>  A B C A 1 1 0 B 0 1 -1 C 1 0 0   A B C A 1 -1 0 B 0 -1 -1 C 1 0 1 </code></pre>  <p>So that output should be</p>  <pre><code>  A B C A 0 -1 0 B 0 -1 0 C 0 0 1 </code></pre>  <p>Values for which <code>matrix 1 == matrix 2</code> will be <code>0</code> and for which <code>matrix1 != matrix2</code> the value of <code>matrix2</code> will be assigned.</p>